											(Laughter)
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>
													<div class="Grid Grid--with-gutter d:f@md p-b:4">
								<div class="Grid__cell d:f h:full m-b:.5 m-b:0@md w:12"></div>

								<div class="Grid__cell flx-s:1 p-r:4">
									<p>
											And all of this is done to some
hoped-for degree of perfection.
											We expect our kids
to perform at a level of perfection
											we were never asked
to perform at ourselves,
